<h1>Studios in <%= current_city.name %></h1>

<% @studios.each do |studio| %>
  <div><h3><%= link_to studio.name, studio_path(studio) %> - <%= studio.street_address %></h3>
    <% if studio.group_classes.first %>
      Classes include: <%= studio.group_classes.map{|gc| gc.name}.join(", ") %>
    <% end %>
  </div><br></br>
<% end %>

Don't see the studio you're looking for? Add a studio <%= link_to "here", new_studio_path %>.
